def plane_seat(a):
    section, seat = a[0:-1], a[-1]
    if not section.isdigit() or int(section) > 60 or seat.upper() not in ' ABCDEFGHK':
        return 'No Seat!!'
    section = 'Front' if int(section) <= 20 else 'Middle' if int(section) <= 40 else 'Back'
    seat = 'Left' if seat.upper() in 'ABC' else 'Middle' if seat.upper() in 'DEF' else 'Right'
    return f'{section}-{seat}'

def plane_seat(a):
    seat_num = a[:-1]
    seat_letter = a[-1].upper()
    if not seat_num.isdigit() or not 1 <= int(seat_num) <= 60 or seat_letter in ['I', 'J'] or not 'A' <= seat_letter <= 'K':
        return 'No Seat!!'
    section = 'Front' if int(seat_num) <= 20 else 'Middle' if int(seat_num) <= 40 else 'Back'
    cluster = 'Left' if 'A' <= seat_letter <= 'C' else 'Middle' if 'D' <= seat_letter <= 'F' else 'Right'
    return f'{section}-{cluster}'

def plane_seat(a):
    num = int(a[:-1])
    letter = a[-1]
    if num < 1 or num > 60 or (letter not in 'ABCDEFGHK'):
        return 'No Seat!!'
    location = 'Front' if num <= 20 else 'Middle' if num <= 40 else 'Back'
    location += '-' + ('Left' if letter in 'ABC' else 'Middle' if letter in 'DEF' else 'Right')
